➜守“连天碧水” 护“清水北送”
http://www.sohu.com/a/412220731_100001675	17868
<p class="ql-align-center">碧水连天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">烟波如画</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200809/5bbc62ab08ff4045b6098a10ea912ef6.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200809/a16e63747e054e149c14587eccefe43e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这是素有“小太平洋”之称的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>丹江口水库</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>也是南水北调中线控制性工程</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>和核心水源区所在地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200809/d7e64ddb432541b896bf494151ab4573.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
